msgid "## Requirements"
msgstr "## 要求"

msgid ""
"Official vllm-ascend images have already included `util-linux` and `procps` /\n"
"`procps-ng` in v0.18.0rc1 and earlier releases. **Starting from v0.18.0rc1, the\n"
"official images also include `numactl`.**"
msgstr ""
"官方 vllm-ascend 镜像在 v0.18.0rc1 及更早版本中已包含 `util-linux` 和 `procps` / `procps-"
"ng`。**从 v0.18.0rc1 开始，官方镜像还包含了 `numactl`。**"

msgid ""
"If you are not using the official image, install the host tools manually:"
msgstr "如果您未使用官方镜像，请手动安装主机工具："

msgid ""
"**Without `numactl` / `migratepages`, vLLM Ascend skips only memory migration.**\n"
"The worker process and runtime threads are still pinned, but pages already\n"
"placed on remote NUMA nodes are not migrated, which **can reduce locality and\n"
"degrade latency or throughput.**"
msgstr ""
"**如果没有 `numactl` / `migratepages`，vLLM Ascend 仅跳过内存迁移。**\n"
"工作进程和运行时线程仍会被绑定，但已放置在远程 NUMA 节点上的页面不会被迁移，这**可能会降低局部性并导致延迟或吞吐量下降。**"

msgid ""
"For optimal locality, use a cpuset that is evenly distributed across NUMA\n"
"nodes. Unbalanced cpusets may reduce the locality benefit of CPU binding."
msgstr "为获得最佳局部性，请使用均匀分布在 NUMA 节点上的 cpuset。不平衡的 cpuset 可能会降低 CPU 绑定的局部性优势。"

msgid ""
"On Ascend 950, CPU binding uses deterministic global CPU slicing because Ascend 950 does not\n"
"report NPU-to-CPU affinity in `npu-smi info -t topo`. Ascend 950 still pins worker,\n"
"ACL, and release threads and can still migrate memory pages when `migratepages`\n"
"is available. Because Ascend 950 skips IRQ binding, it does not reserve the first two\n"
"CPUs in each NPU pool for IRQ handling. Those CPUs are assigned to the main\n"
"worker instead."
msgstr ""
"在 Ascend 950 上，CPU 绑定使用确定性的全局 CPU 切片，因为 Ascend 950 不在 `npu-smi info -t topo`"
" 中报告 NPU 到 CPU 的亲和性。Ascend 950 仍然会绑定工作进程、ACL 和释放线程，并且在 `migratepages` "
"可用时仍可迁移内存页面。由于 Ascend 950 跳过了 IRQ 绑定，它不会在每个 NPU 池中保留前两个 CPU 用于 IRQ 处理。这些 CPU"
" 将被分配给主工作进程。"

msgid ""
"For IRQ binding, the process also needs permission to read `/proc/interrupts`\n"
"and write `/proc/irq/*/smp_affinity`. If `irqbalance` is running and the process\n"
"can use `systemctl`, vLLM Ascend stops it before applying IRQ affinity. In\n"
"containers where `systemctl` is unavailable, stop `irqbalance` on the host when\n"
"IRQ affinity matters."
msgstr ""
"对于 IRQ 绑定，进程还需要读取 `/proc/interrupts` 和写入 `/proc/irq/*/smp_affinity` 的权限。如果 "
"`irqbalance` 正在运行且进程可以使用 `systemctl`，vLLM Ascend 会在应用 IRQ 亲和性之前停止它。在 "
"`systemctl` 不可用的容器中，当 IRQ 亲和性重要时，请在主机上停止 `irqbalance`。"

msgid ""
"Ascend 950 does not apply IRQ binding. When running on Ascend 950, the log contains\n"
"`[irq] IRQ binding skipped on Ascend 950.` and no `/proc/irq/*/smp_affinity` files are\n"
"written by this feature."
msgstr ""
"Ascend 950 不应用 IRQ 绑定。在 Ascend 950 上运行时，日志包含 `[irq] IRQ binding skipped on "
"Ascend 950.`，并且此功能不会写入任何 `/proc/irq/*/smp_affinity` 文件。"

msgid ""
"On the host, stop `irqbalance` before starting vLLM when you need stable IRQ\n"
"affinity:"
msgstr "在主机上，当您需要稳定的 IRQ 亲和性时，请在启动 vLLM 之前停止 `irqbalance`："

msgid ""
"After the vLLM service exits, restart it if the host should return to the\n"
"default IRQ balancing policy:"
msgstr "vLLM 服务退出后，如果主机应恢复到默认的 IRQ 平衡策略，请重新启动它："

msgid "## Troubleshooting"
msgstr "## 故障排除"

msgid ""
"| Message | Meaning | Action |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| `CPU binding skipped: non-ARM CPU detected.` | CPU binding only runs on ARM. | No action needed on x86_64. |\n"
"| `Can not get running npu info.` | No running NPU was found, or `ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` filtered all NPUs. | Check visible NPU IDs and `npu-smi info`. |\n"
"| `Insufficient CPUs for binding...` | Fewer CPUs are available than the role split requires. Devices with IRQ binding need at least 5 CPUs per logical NPU; Ascend 950 needs at least 3. | Expand the cpuset or reduce visible NPUs. |\n"
"| `NPU topo affinity not found...` | Topology affinity is unavailable. | vLLM Ascend falls back to `global_slice`; check `npu-smi info -t topo` only if topology affinity is expected on this device. |\n"
"| `The 'migratepages' command is not available...` | Memory migration is skipped, while CPU thread binding still proceeds. | Install `numactl` if NUMA locality or performance is affected. |\n"
"| `[irq] IRQ binding skipped on Ascend 950.` | Ascend 950 does not use the IRQ binding step. | No action needed. Worker, ACL, release thread binding and memory migration still proceed. |\n"
"| `Bind cpus failed in rank...` | A binding step failed and CPU binding was skipped for that rank. | Check `taskset`, `lscpu`, `npu-smi`, cpuset size, and `/proc/irq` permissions. |"
msgstr ""
"| 消息 | 含义 | 操作 |\n"
"| --- | --- | --- |\n"
"| `CPU binding skipped: non-ARM CPU detected.` | CPU 绑定仅在 ARM 上运行。 | x86_64 上无需操作。 |\n"
"| `Can not get running npu info.` | 未找到正在运行的 NPU，或 `ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` 过滤了所有 NPU。 | 检查可见的 NPU ID 和 `npu-smi info`。 |\n"
"| `Insufficient CPUs for binding...` | 可用 CPU 数量少于角色拆分所需。需要 IRQ 绑定的设备每个逻辑 NPU 至少需要 5 个 CPU；Ascend 950 至少需要 3 个。 | 扩展 cpuset 或减少可见的 NPU。 |\n"
"| `NPU topo affinity not found...` | 拓扑亲和性不可用。 | vLLM Ascend 回退到 `global_slice`；仅当此设备上预期有拓扑亲和性时，才检查 `npu-smi info -t topo`。 |\n"
"| `The 'migratepages' command is not available...` | 跳过内存迁移，但 CPU 线程绑定仍继续。 | 如果 NUMA 局部性或性能受到影响，请安装 `numactl`。 |\n"
"| `[irq] IRQ binding skipped on Ascend 950.` | Ascend 950 不使用 IRQ 绑定步骤。 | 无需操作。工作进程、ACL、释放线程绑定和内存迁移仍将继续。 |\n"
"| `Bind cpus failed in rank...` | 绑定步骤失败，该 rank 的 CPU 绑定被跳过。 | 检查 `taskset`、`lscpu`、`npu-smi`、cpuset 大小和 `/proc/irq` 权限。 |"

